05:40.380 --> 05:41.610
(phone ringing, Kurt groans)

05:41.611 --> 05:42.931
Look, I know this is frustrating.

05:42.965 --> 05:44.266
It's frustrating for me, too,

05:44.300 --> 05:45.934
