could be a career for me.

05:49.722 --> 05:51.440
I get that; I-I do.

05:51.474 --> 05:52.724
I really get it.

05:52.775 --> 05:54.342
It's just...

05:54.360 --> 05:57.178
I... really miss you.

05:57.196 --> 05:59.281
A lot, okay?

05:59.315 --> 06:01.115
I miss talking to you
and I miss hugging you

06:01.116 --> 06:02.734
and I miss messing around with you...

06:02.785 --> 06:04.686
Me, too.

06:04.704 --> 06:06.738
But you're coming in two weeks, right?

06:06.789 --> 06:10.358
I know, but... what am I
supposed to do until then,

06:10.376 --> 06:11.910
just hold my breath?

06:11.961 --> 06:13.128
(phone ringing)

06:13.162 --> 06:15.747
Shoot. Joan Didion's calling.

06:15.798 --> 06:17.365
She always has the best gossip.

06:17.383 --> 06:19.367
Um, all right, I will call you or text you

06:19.385 --> 06:20.368
on a break, okay? Okay.

06:20.386 --> 06:22.054
Okay. I love you.

06:24.390 --> 06:26.725
