<i>Look at her, she's amazing.</i>

06:30.229 --> 06:31.930
<i>Even when she's not all dolled up.</i>

06:31.981 --> 06:34.149
<i>I've never seen her so alive.</i>

06:34.183 --> 06:36.268
<i>She's found the place where she belongs,</i>

06:36.319 --> 06:38.052
<i>where she thrives.</i>

06:38.071 --> 06:40.054
<i>I just wish I could find a place for me</i>

06:40.073 --> 06:41.907
<i>because I definitely don't belong here.</i>

06:41.941 --> 06:43.825
<i>I'd never get into NYADA,</i>
<i>and what the hell</i>

06:43.860 --> 06:45.727
<i>am I gonna do in New York,</i>

06:45.745 --> 06:48.396
<i>run a hot dog cart outside</i>
<i>of Madison Square Garden?</i>

06:48.414 --> 06:50.115
<i>No way.</i>

06:50.166 --> 06:52.000
<i>I used to be the man of her dreams,</i>

06:52.034 --> 06:55.737
