sing "Don't Stop Believin',"

09:53.251 --> 09:54.491
or something equally uplifting.

09:54.492 --> 09:55.452
I don't... I don't know.

09:55.471 --> 09:57.791
I'm so out of practice, I
haven't even sang in the shower

09:57.792 --> 09:59.437
