10:10.733 --> 10:12.333
I know, I just couldn't wait any longer.

10:12.334 --> 10:13.201
I miss you too much.

10:13.235 --> 10:15.153
Oh, I miss you, too.
So good to see you.

10:15.204 --> 10:16.655
Wait!
I can't believe you're here.

10:16.706 --> 10:17.706
I missed you so much. Hi.

10:17.707 --> 10:19.291
Hi. Oh, Finn!

10:19.325 --> 10:20.959
What are you doing here?

10:20.993 --> 10:23.662
I'm... not really sure
at the moment, but...

10:23.713 --> 10:25.630
