11:16.911 --> 11:18.659
But I'm not a student, so...

11:18.693 --> 11:21.161
Well, you're with Rachel,
which makes you honorary.

11:21.195 --> 11:23.075
And I'm buddies
with Pascal, the piano player.

11:23.076 --> 11:24.756
And the song works better as a duet, so...

11:24.757 --> 11:27.534
Well, why don't you guys sing it together?

11:27.585 --> 11:29.670
It's a NYADA tradition, right?
And you guys

11:29.704 --> 11:30.671
are both NYADA students.

11:30.705 --> 11:32.322
Finn.

11:32.340 --> 11:33.373
Yeah.

11:33.424 --> 11:35.208
All right, let's do it.

11:39.297 --> 11:41.264
I love you.

11:44.435 --> 11:45.802
Wish me luck.

11:48.106 --> 11:50.173
